data.title: PGA of Canada
data.meta_description: A membership-based non-profit association representing over 3,700 club professionals across Canada founded on July 11, 1911, which makes the PGA of Canada the 2nd.
data.text:
Alan McLean nearly records first 59 in PGA of Canada National Championship history, fires 60 to take six-stroke lead

McLean makes eight birdies and two eagles to take six-stroke lead into final round of the PGA Seniors’ Championship of Canada presented by GOLFTEC over Marc Hurtubise, Dennis Hendershott and Gordon Burns.

More

Gord Burns makes 11 birdies on Tuesday to lead PGA Seniors’ Championship of Canada presented by GOLFTEC

After turning 50 late last year, Gord Burns wasted little time showing what he is made of to the rest of the field at the PGA Seniors’ Championship of Canada presented by GOLFTEC, making 11 birdies on his way to an opening-round 62.
